The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Sports | Chawla hopeful
                                                   Chawla hopeful
            OUR SPECIAL CORRESPONDENT                      
	New Delhi: Piyush Chawla thinks a good performance in the Champions League could help him to make a comeback to the national team.         
	Chawla, who will be playing for Sussex Sharks, said: I would try to use my experience and local knowledge to help my team. It is also a big event for me. I know national selectors would be watching all the Indian players closely, he said.                                                                                                                       
